## Example 5 — Evaluate Trigonometric Expressions

Find `cos(10pi/3)`.

Use periodicity:

`cos(10pi/3) = cos(4pi/3 + 2pi) = cos(4pi/3)`

From the unit circle:

`cos(4pi/3) = -1/2`

So:

`cos(10pi/3) = -1/2`

